Text.SourceString: Hello, I don' think I've seen yeh 'round here before.
Text.LocalizedString: Hello, I don' think I've seen yeh 'round here before.

Text.SourceString: 'ave a good day, now.
Text.LocalizedString: 'ave a good day, now.

Text.SourceString: We just got a fresh batch o' petalia seeds in. They're sellin' like hotcakes, they are.
Text.LocalizedString: We just got a fresh batch o' petalia seeds in. They're sellin' like hotcakes, they are.

Text.SourceString: Gotta keep an eye on the stock of manirip. Some of them are already getting old.
Text.LocalizedString: Gotta keep an eye on the stock of manirip. Some of them are already getting old.

Text.SourceString: Thinkin' of bringin' in some rare coral spices next week. They'll be a treat for the cookin' folks.
Text.LocalizedString: Thinkin' of bringin' in some rare coral spices next week. They'll be a treat for the cookin' folks.

Text.SourceString: Hello! Lookin' for somethin' special today, are yeh? Maybe some of our seeds?
Text.LocalizedString: Hello! Lookin' for somethin' special today, are yeh? Maybe some of our seeds?

Text.SourceString: If yeh need any help findin' what yeh're after, just give a shout. I'm always 'ere to lend a hand.
Text.LocalizedString: If yeh need any help findin' what yeh're after, just give a shout. I'm always 'ere to lend a hand.

Text.SourceString: See yeh found our selection of crops. They're top-notch.
Text.LocalizedString: See yeh found our selection of crops. They're top-notch.

Text.SourceString: There's a stone carving contest comin' up in the North Sea. We're thinkin' of settin' up a stall there with some goodies.
Text.LocalizedString: There's a stone carving contest comin' up in the North Sea. We're thinkin' of settin' up a stall there with some goodies.

Text.SourceString: The colder season drawin' near. We should start preparin' for that.
Text.LocalizedString: The colder season drawin' near. We should start preparin' for that.

Text.SourceString: This season's sea spuds are lookin' mighty fine. Perfect for a hearty stew.
Text.LocalizedString: This season's sea spuds are lookin' mighty fine. Perfect for a hearty stew.

Text.SourceString: Lawu's got some sea lettuce for dinner. Crisp and fresh, straight from the North Sea.
Text.LocalizedString: Lawu's got some sea lettuce for dinner. Crisp and fresh, straight from the North Sea.

Text.SourceString: If yeh're lookin' for somethin' to spice up your meals, try chilies. They've got a real kick.
Text.LocalizedString: If yeh're lookin' for somethin' to spice up your meals, try chilies. They've got a real kick.

Text.SourceString: They're from up there, you've heard of it, haven't you?
Text.LocalizedString: They're from up there, you've heard of it, haven't you?

Text.SourceString: Lawu and I are plannin' a small trip to the surface. Heard there's some interestin' things to see.
Text.LocalizedString: Lawu and I are plannin' a small trip to the surface. Heard there's some interestin' things to see.

Text.SourceString: In me spare time, I've been learnin' a bit of sea-sculpting. Keeps the hands busy, it does.
Text.LocalizedString: In me spare time, I've been learnin' a bit of sea-sculpting. Keeps the hands busy, it does.

Text.SourceString: Lawu's been workin' on a new recipe. Wait till yeh try her sea burger. It's divine!
Text.LocalizedString: Lawu's been workin' on a new recipe. Wait till yeh try her sea burger. It's divine!

Text.SourceString: Business has been a bit slow with the currents changin', but we're holdin' our own.
Text.LocalizedString: Business has been a bit slow with the currents changin', but we're holdin' our own.

Text.SourceString: There's talk of a new trade route openin' up. Might be good for the store, bringin' in new customers.
Text.LocalizedString: There's talk of a new trade route openin' up. Might be good for the store, bringin' in new customers.

Text.SourceString: We're thinkin' of expandin' our delivery service, reach out to more distant parts of the kingdom.
Text.LocalizedString: We're thinkin' of expandin' our delivery service, reach out to more distant parts of the kingdom.

Text.SourceString: There's a rumor goin' 'round about a rare fish sightin' near the gate. Exciting!
Text.LocalizedString: There's a rumor goin' 'round about a rare fish sightin' near the gate. Exciting!

Text.SourceString: If yeh're havin' trouble with your sea crops, try givin' 'em a bit more light. Works wonders, it does.
Text.LocalizedString: If yeh're havin' trouble with your sea crops, try givin' 'em a bit more light. Works wonders, it does.

Text.SourceString: When arrangin' your garden, remember to give 'em plenty of room. They like to spread out a bit.
Text.LocalizedString: When arrangin' your garden, remember to give 'em plenty of room. They like to spread out a bit.

Text.SourceString: Meh! What do I know, I don't even have one myself. Do what you want.
Text.LocalizedString: Meh! What do I know, I don't even have one myself. Do what you want.

Text.SourceString: We're teamin' up with a local carver for some unique store decorations... <NPCName>Galoong</> and <NPCName>Vihren</>, you know them? Yeh'll love 'em.
Text.LocalizedString: We're teamin' up with a local carver for some unique store decorations... <NPCName>Galoong</> and <NPCName>Vihren</>, you know them? Yeh'll love 'em.

Text.SourceString: There's a seaweed weaver in the North Reefs we're workin' with. Makes the most beautiful mats.
Text.LocalizedString: There's a seaweed weaver in the North Reefs we're workin' with. Makes the most beautiful mats.

Text.SourceString: Now, you hear, it's the North Reefs, not the North Sea. The one in the North Sea? Messy craftsmanship.
Text.LocalizedString: Now, you hear, it's the North Reefs, not the North Sea. The one in the North Sea? Messy craftsmanship.

Text.SourceString: Been talkin' to a pearl diver from the deep sea – the slug – about gettin' some exclusive items for the store. They'll be a real treasure.
Text.LocalizedString: Been talkin' to a pearl diver from the deep sea – the slug – about gettin' some exclusive items for the store. They'll be a real treasure.

Text.SourceString: We're thinkin' of ways to diversify the store's offerings, you know, to keep up with the ever-changin' market demands.
Text.LocalizedString: We're thinkin' of ways to diversify the store's offerings, you know, to keep up with the ever-changin' market demands.

Text.SourceString: The increase in tariffs on imported sea goods has us rethinkin' our supply lines. Gotta keep things affordable for our folks.
Text.LocalizedString: The increase in tariffs on imported sea goods has us rethinkin' our supply lines. Gotta keep things affordable for our folks.

Text.SourceString: Some say there's a boom comin' in the sea silk trade. Might be wise to get in on that before it's all the rage.
Text.LocalizedString: Some say there's a boom comin' in the sea silk trade. Might be wise to get in on that before it's all the rage.

Text.SourceString: This year's harvest of sea grapes is lookin' mighty fine. They're a staple in my grotto.
Text.LocalizedString: This year's harvest of sea grapes is lookin' mighty fine. They're a staple in my grotto.

Text.SourceString: Our seaweed varieties are second to none. I take pride in sourcin' the best for our customers.
Text.LocalizedString: Our seaweed varieties are second to none. I take pride in sourcin' the best for our customers.

Text.SourceString: When I'm not at the store, I love takin' <NPCName>Lawu</> to explore the coral forests. Family time is precious, you know.
Text.LocalizedString: When I'm not at the store, I love takin' <NPCName>Lawu</> to explore the coral forests. Family time is precious, you know.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Lawu</> and I have been workin' on a recipe book together. It's filled with all sorts of traditional merfolk dishes.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Lawu</> and I have been workin' on a recipe book together. It's filled with all sorts of traditional merfolk dishes.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, I wonder what it'd be like to stroll on a beach, feel the sand 'neath my feet, not just my fins.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, I wonder what it'd be like to stroll on a beach, feel the sand 'neath my feet, not just my fins.

Text.SourceString: I've heard tales of mountains that touch the sky. Imagine that!
Text.LocalizedString: I've heard tales of mountains that touch the sky. Imagine that!

Text.SourceString: What I wouldn't give to see a sunset from above the water. They say it's like the whole sky's on fire.
Text.LocalizedString: What I wouldn't give to see a sunset from above the water. They say it's like the whole sky's on fire.

Text.SourceString: Imagine eatin' food that ain't from the sea. Heard they have things called 'fruits' growin' on trees!
Text.LocalizedString: Imagine eatin' food that ain't from the sea. Heard they have things called 'fruits' growin' on trees!

Text.SourceString: I fancy the idea of a walk in a forest. Not a kelp forest, mind, but one with trees and birds and all that.
Text.LocalizedString: I fancy the idea of a walk in a forest. Not a kelp forest, mind, but one with trees and birds and all that.

Text.SourceString: Heard 'bout these things called 'bicycles.' Fancy swimmin' through the air on two wheels, eh?
Text.LocalizedString: Heard 'bout these things called 'bicycles.' Fancy swimmin' through the air on two wheels, eh?

Text.SourceString: Someone told me 'bout 'snow.' Thought it was like our sea foam, but cold and fluffy. Can yeh imagine?
Text.LocalizedString: Someone told me 'bout 'snow.' Thought it was like our sea foam, but cold and fluffy. Can yeh imagine?

Text.SourceString: I got this 'watch' from a surface trader. Turns out it don't tell yeh where to swim, just the time of day!
Text.LocalizedString: I got this 'watch' from a surface trader. Turns out it don't tell yeh where to swim, just the time of day!

Text.SourceString: So, they have these big metal birds in the sky, 'planes' they call 'em. Fly without fins or tails, how's that work?
Text.LocalizedString: So, they have these big metal birds in the sky, 'planes' they call 'em. Fly without fins or tails, how's that work?

Text.SourceString: The princess, she told me a bit 'bout it, but didn't go into much detail, did she? That right?
Text.LocalizedString: The princess, she told me a bit 'bout it, but didn't go into much detail, did she? That right?

Text.SourceString: Yeh got one of them 'watches' on ya?
Text.LocalizedString: Yeh got one of them 'watches' on ya?

Text.SourceString: Oh, yeh should've seen it, I traded a hefty piece of coral from me grotto for this 'watch.' <NPCName>Lawu</>, she wasn't too pleased for a while.//We got to stay in the barracks a bit longer.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, yeh should've seen it, I traded a hefty piece of coral from me grotto for this 'watch.' <NPCName>Lawu</>, she wasn't too pleased for a while.//We got to stay in the barracks a bit longer.
